  "title": "Safety Coordinator (Manufacturing)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>MNC (Manufacturing)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $3000 to $4000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: North (SINGAPORE)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8.30am – 5.30pm (Mon – Fri)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Scope</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Conduct regular site safety inspections and follow up on corrective actions.</strong></li>\n  <li>Identify hazards, unsafe conditions/behaviours and recommend practical control measures.</li>\n  <li><strong>Support incident and near-miss investigations and ensure closure of action items.</strong></li>\n  <li>Assist in Permit-To-Work (PTW) and Safety Induction Course (SIC) checks and trainings.</li>\n  <li><strong>Support risk assessment reviews and documentation checks (e.g. Method Statements, competency certificates).</strong></li>\n  <li>Coordinate with employees and contractors to ensure compliance with company safety rules and legal requirements.</li>\n  <li><strong>Conduct toolbox meetings and support safety campaigns and awareness activities.</strong></li>\n  <li>Report non-compliance and support rectification with relevant departments.</li>\n  <li><strong>Stop unsafe work when necessary.</strong></li>\n  <li>Perform any other safety-related duties assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Higher Nitec or Diploma in Engineering or related fields</li>\n  <li><strong>Safety &amp; Health related training preferred (e.g. Advanced Certificate in Workplace Safety &amp; Health – Workplace Safety Level B)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
